    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the marque, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS system functioning flawlessly. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, benefiting from proactive rear subframe reinforcement and a precision-tuned suspension. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been maintained to an exacting standard, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency and a linear power band. The exterior finish and interior ergonomics are preserved in a state that reflects true collector-grade stewardship.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Zero cosmetic flaws. Mechanical systems perfect. Service records available. Garage kept.",
